Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.89,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,In 1940, the Tacoma\NNarrows Bridge looked
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.24,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,like the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.60,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It was long,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.97,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,slender, cheaper than the\Noriginal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,conservative design, and\Nbeautiful enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.80,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,to make its movement\Nfamous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,People called it Galloping\NGertie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:22.12,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But the wind on collapse\Nday was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.48,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,not extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.84,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The bridge had already
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:26.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,survived stronger autumn\Nwinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:29.40,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The hidden problem was\Nwhat the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:31.34,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,did to the air after it\Nstarted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:32.58,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.82,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Its shallow solid\Nplate-girder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:35.91,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,deck was too flexible in\Ntorsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.11,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Once the roadway began to\Ntwist,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.33,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,the motion changed the\Nairflow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:42.90,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,and the changed airflow\Nfed the next
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.58,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.26,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Engineers were studying\Nthe motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:48.07,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,but the design culture had\Nnot yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.39,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,made dynamic aerodynamic\Ntesting routine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.55,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,for bridges like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.17,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The bridge did not just\Nmeet wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:56.80,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It entered a behavior its\Nown design
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,made possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.68,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:01.79,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,consequences.
